items.sentence: I couldn't do the things that I wanted to do.
I thought that Tom shouldn't do that outside.
I know Tom doesn't want to do that with Mary.
I doubt Tom really has time to do that today.
I was surprised that Tom wasn't at the party.
I'm wondering whether that's going to happen.
Tom will likely want to go to Boston with us.
I don't think I could get used to this noise.
I don't think I could get used to this smell.
Tom realized he had fallen in love with Mary.
